RT @ChicagoSports: Tyler Chatwood tied a career high with 11 strikeouts in 6⅔ shutout innings, and the Cubs held on for a 4-3 win over the Pirates at Wrigley Field.

Ian Happ and Javier Baez hit solo home runs, and Kyle Schwarber added a two-run blast for the Cubs (6-2).
